00:52:24.849 --> 00:52:27.489
I think it's Armageddon.

00:52:27.489 --> 00:52:30.050
He said was coming soon.

00:52:30.050 --> 00:52:32.610
And he remembered Harold writing horseback

00:52:32.610 --> 00:52:35.130
50 years ago in that territory.

00:52:35.130 --> 00:52:36.449
And he got there again.

00:52:38.289 --> 00:52:41.769
